data.description: This stunning 4-bedroom, 3.5-bath quad-level home boasts an updated open floor plan. The kitchen is a chef's dream with a spacious granite L-shaped island featuring a breakfast bar, larger cabinets with granite tops and backsplash, stainless steel double range oven, microwave, and a generous farmhouse sink under a skylight. The main-level family room offers a cozy gas starter wood-burning fireplace and opens to a large deck and patio. Convenient 1st-floor laundry room. The fantastic lower-level family room, bedroom, and full bath make it ideal for related living. Don't forget the generously sized unfinished sub-basement, ready for your personal touch or for extra storage. Being sold as is
